# Spoilage Solution

A lightweight **Factorio** mod that introduces smart solutions to spoilage — keep your items fresh and preserved for longer!

> 🔧 Category: Tweaks  
> 🧊 Version: 2.0  
> 📦 Downloads: 1,400+  

---

## ✨ Features

**Spoilage Solution** adds two new mechanics to help you avoid spoilage of perishable items:

1. **🥫 Canning** – Preserve cans for extended storage.
2. **❄️ Cryogenic Freezing** – Store items in ultra-low temperatures to prevent spoilage altogether.
